original_title: Pieter Tiddens: Vooruit! Nog Één Keer Kindercabaret, Nu Nog Anders!
overview: A comedy show for children by the Dutch cabaret artist (and actor and singer and musician) Pieter Tiddens. The show is about the mutability of life. Why can't things stay as they are?
title: Pieter Tiddens: Vooruit! Nog Één Keer Kindercabaret, Nu Nog Anders!
